  <brief_title>Dissecting the Role of Distal Embolization of Athero-thrombotic Material in Primary PCI: the ThrombOticBurden and mIcrovAscularobStruction (TOBIAS) Study.</brief_title>
  <acronym>TOBIAS</acronym>
