  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      demonstrate that FD-OCT guidance is feasible and possibly results in reduction of
      frequency-domain Optical Coherence Tomography-defined residual thrombus burden after
      thrombus-aspiration.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
